{"tid":1976881,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[文化歷史台]第一講:黑人棺材舞","createTime":"2020-04-17T14:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T14:08:33.000Z","uid":74954,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd23d55692e3f58a7256c3ca83bad64198a8ceb","tid":1976881,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T14:08:33.000Z","msg":"有另一個相同post 可以唔理佢<br />\n由佢沉底先  以後開番係呢個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者前言:<br />\n話說岩岩2019年歷史系畢業無耐 開始番工覺得自己番工番到無咩人生意義，番既工完全同以前讀既書無任何關係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟想學以致用，將以前學到既知識，為大家做唔同題材既歷史同文化研究，內容設計簡白易明，希望令到大家學新智識唔洗再局限係書入邊咁悶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一講:非洲棺材舞片文化研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REsy7pE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREsy7pE.jpg&h=fe33303f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0OrvHsJMVs&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW0OrvHsJMVs%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU94R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=e4ddcc61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W0OrvHsJMVs&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文字版精華要點<br />\n第一講重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.非洲棺材舞片呢條meme 既出處係非洲迦納<br />\n2.棺材舞唔係佢地傳統文化<br />\n3.當地人點睇:認為棺材舞係好事<br />\n4.棺材外型無話做唔到，只有你諗唔到<br />\n5.棺材舞重點意義在於遊街同跳舞，係十分尊重死者既行為<br />\n6. 林鄭壽終正寢 大家可以一齊幫佢跳棺材舞   以示尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一講<br />\n會講大熱電影文化<br />\n近代喪屍片起源研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n製作需時<br />\n敬請期待"}]}